@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ldcbze(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs((0.59 - (v0 + 0.30 + v1 + 0.33)))
    v2 = ((0.13 + (v0 + 0.17 * tmp + 0.07)) + v1)
    v2 = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.26 + tmp + 0.04) / (v2 + 0.67 * tmp + 0.29)))
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
